{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *JIRA Server*. Using *JIRA Cloud*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JRACLOUD-16875].
  {panel}

It would be great if you could enable the CreateCustomField Jelly Tag to add new contexts with it. If not then a new jelly tag to edit custom fields and then add new contexts to it.

UseCase:

 A select custom field with different drop down values for different projects. The need for Jelly script is when you have 40 odd drop down values for each custom field. Even the UI doesn't have an option of adding all the 40 values at one go. You have to sit and add each value one by one. This is really painful.

