  {panel}

Would like the ability to customize notifications sent to Reporter and to Assignee when a ticket is created. Currently, both receive the same notification.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *JIRA Server*. Using *JIRA Cloud*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JRACLOUD-16814].
  {panel}

We have users with issues containing a dozen or more subtasks.  They would like to have the ability to navigate between subtasks directly, much like the Issue Navigator, without having to travel back up the tree to the main issue.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *JIRA Server*. Using *JIRA Cloud*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JRACLOUD-16812].
  {panel}

Plugin developers who wish to write func tests could benefit from our func test framework be made public (or shipping it with JIRA source).  Before this can happen, probably a lot of cleanup and documentation would have to happen.
